    <item>
      <title>Enable XML for Android App access to Wordpress</title>
      <link>http://www.ifconfig.it/hugo/post/enable-xml-for-android-app-access-to-wordpress/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Dec 2011 16:27:07 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.ifconfig.it/hugo/post/enable-xml-for-android-app-access-to-wordpress/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you get an error when configuring &lt;a href=&#34;http://android.wordpress.org/&#34;&gt;Wordpress app for Android&lt;/a&gt;, log into your WordPress blog and in the admin area go to Settings -&amp;gt; Writing and under Remote Publishing you&amp;rsquo;ll see a checkbox for XML-RPC. Check that, click &amp;lsquo;Save Changes&amp;rsquo; and XML-RPC services will be turned on for your blog.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
